title.rendered: Alticor Inc Supports Big Brother Big Sister

content.rendered: Alticor Inc’ Pacific District supported the Big Brother Big Sister Revenge of the Nerds Bowl For Kids’ Sake fundraiser in Aiea, Hawaii. The district office and five job sites participated in this annual event, which raises money to support Big Brothers Big Sisters as they change children’s lives.
